Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real mess, just like the rumors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A graveyard of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a battle here \Nduring ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dear ancestors sure blew each other to hell and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.96,0:00:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,These things barely resemble ships anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job is to look for any \Nusable ships we can salvage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget's orders, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still a bust, however you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.38,0:01:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The few ships that survived intact have already rusted away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been searching for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's about time we gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm below you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look too heavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good catch, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May I go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cargo vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been down here for some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's surprisingly well-preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A core unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make a new Yunboro with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How's the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the stern. No apparent damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She might've been scuttled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with the bow. It's a joy to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Hey, Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.74,0:02:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it doesn't work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you really care about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Researching the ancient civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Archeology," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can restore some of the data, \NI might find out more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world people lived in \Nwhen this ship was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to bring all that stuff \Nto the surface too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge trench!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We can pass under the bilge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we can pull cables \Nunder it with the Yunboros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we found one heck of a haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
