Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.86,0:51:06.52,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}We pursue the same dream now
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.52,0:51:12.49,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}kimi no hohaba wa watashi yori ookikute
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.52,0:51:12.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Your gait might be a little long for me
