Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.49,0:51:19.14,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}The truly important things are invisible to the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.14,0:51:25.50,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}tsunaida sono te tsuyoku nigitta
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.14,0:51:25.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}That's why I held your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.50,0:51:31.65,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}hon no sukoshi mae made shiranakatta kimi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.50,0:51:31.65,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}I only came to know you recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.65,0:51:40.16,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}ima konna ni mo kakegae nai hitori natteku
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.65,0:51:40.16,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}and you're already irreplaceable to me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.16,0:51:46.45,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}wasurenaide ne itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.16,0:51:46.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Don't forget, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.45,0:51:52.77,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}yorokobi mo kanashimi mo wakeaitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.45,0:51:52.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}I want to share everything with you
